'''''Inklings: Jahrbuch für Literatur und Ästhetik''''' (English: "Annual Review of Literature and Aesthetics") is a journal focussing on studies of fantastic literature and the [[Inklings]]. It has been published by the Inklings Gesellschaft on a regular basis since [[1983]], and contains articles both in German and English.<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.inklings-gesellschaft.de/jahrbucher/|articlename=Jahrbücher/Inklings Yearbooks|dated=|website=[http://www.inklings-gesellschaft.de/ Inklings-Gesellschaft.de]|accessed=25 June 2012}}</ref>
